''See also [[arrivé]]''
==English==
===Pronunciation===
*ə-rīv', /əˈraɪv/, /@"raIv/

===Verb===
'''to arrive''' ([[arrives]], [[arrived]], [[arriving]])

# to [[reach]]
#: ''We have arrived here''
# to [[get]] to a [[certain]] [[place]]
#: ''We arrived and booked in''.
# to [[obtain]] a [[level]] of [[success]] or [[fame]].
#: ''He had finally arrived on Broadway.''

====Antonyms====
*[[depart]]

